(98, 1, '2022-12-22 23:29:13', '2022-12-22 16:29:13', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>⚔️ Dark Knight</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">✪ Introduce</span></h3>\r\nThe Dark Knights are dedicated Warriors who train constantly to perfect their sword skills.\r\n\r\nThey translate their Agility and High Fitness stats into frontal and regional attacks such as: Twisted Slash, Death Stab, and Rageful Blow\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-96 size-full\" src=\"https://mu.tienlinhmobile.games/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/z3981041185341_bf820c046a3ab623a9ff310dea71f209.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1788\" height=\"1004\" />\r\n\r\nAlong the golden age, every generation of the class of Dark Knight had been protecting civilians of MU continent. Though, the period has long passed. Wars have made them exhausted and gradually they began to abandon the missions. A part of them wanders around to train their skills to be the best, while the rest goes on and try to bring justice to people. But their fates remain, Dark Knight class will always plunge into deadly battles.\r\n\r\nDark Knight class is the symbol of strength and power. In the fierce battles, they can defeat other characters even when they are seriously injured. Based on their excellent vitality, Dark Knight characters are capable of venturing alone without any difficulty. He can wear different types of armor, use different weapons such as sword, hammer or spear. Dark Knight class’ skills do not consume too much energy, but they require good equipment and accessory to maximize their strength.\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">✪ Basic Properties</span></h3>\r\nStats Analysis Ratio Without Equipment (5 Stars as the Highest; 1 Star as the Lowest; ✨: Half Star)\r\n\r\n<span id=\"input_part_2\" class=\"\" data-mention=\" : half star)\"></span>P-DMG: ⭐️⭐️⭐️\r\nM-DMG: ⭐️\r\nP-DEF: ⭐️\r\nM-DEF: ⭐️\r\nHP: ⭐️✨\r\nACCURACY: ⭐️\r\nAVADE: ⭐️\r\n\r\n<strong>For any questions and support requests, players ca