(210, 1, '2022-12-24 22:54:30', '2022-12-24 15:54:30', '<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xhhsvwb xat24cr xgzva0m xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\"><strong>⚔️</strong></span> <strong>ELF</strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">✪ Introduce</span></h3>\r\nThe Elf of Noria is a character of ancient clans. They claim that they are the first line of MU continent before both humans and orcs. An Elf in Noria has reported that they have a magical and graceful beauty. Although they seem to avoid battles, it can not be said that they are shy. The Elves taught people the skills of using the bow. No one can defeat the Elf class in a battle with a bow. The Elves of Noria also had covenants with other clans and those pacts drew them into wars.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-178 size-full\" src=\"https://mu.tienlinhmobile.games/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/z3986042599768_cbf6e046c9a470109176854d2974ab74.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1788\" height=\"1004\" />Elves’ abilities are an integral part of a party. Elf class’ energy can do spells such as defense boosting, power-up, or health recovery. Elf class’ power astonishes ranged fighters, their quick attacks and high evasive ability make them excellent hand-to-hand combatants.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">✪ Basic Properties</span></h3>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Stats Analysis Ratio Without Equipment (5 Stars as the Highest; 1 Star as the Lowest; ✨: Half Star)</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">P-DMG: ⭐️✨</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">M-DMG: ⭐️✨</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">P-DEF: ⭐️<span class=\"x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xhhsvwb xat24cr xgzva0m xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\">⭐️</span></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">M-DEF: ⭐️<span class=\"x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xhhsvwb xat24cr xgzv