(301, 1, '2022-12-27 08:48:25', '2022-12-27 01:48:25', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xhhsvwb xat24cr xgzva0m xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od\"><strong>⚔️</strong></span> <strong>Holy Mage</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">✪ Introduce</span></h3>\r\nThe Holy Mage is the leader of the Holy Light and specializes in using holy magic to purify herself by removing any debuffs, while also buffing party members and healing them, making her the real mainstay of the team in PvP.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-302\" src=\"https://mu.tienlinhmobile.games/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/z3991174027485_5ca4ee6b6e5c59bf907001a4532ef6cf.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1788\" height=\"1004\" />\r\n\r\nWith the new Master Skill, players can decide between leveling up or investing their experience points to boost the ATK, HP, or DEF of their character.\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">✪ Basic Properties</span></h3>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Stats Analysis Ratio Without Equipment (5 Stars as the Highest; 1 Star as the Lowest; ✨: Half Star)</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">P-DMG: ⭐️⭐️</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">M-DMG: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">P-DEF: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">M-DEF: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">HP: ⭐️⭐️⭐️</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">ACCURACY: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">AVADE: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">\r\n\r\n<strong>For any questions and support requests, players can contact the Admin via the following ways</strong>:\r\n<div id=\"bb_msg_id_1662819634779\" class=\"chat-message wrap-message rotate-container \" data-node-type=\"bubble-message\">\r\n<div cla