/div>\n</div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>IV. EXCHANGE</strong></span></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong> 1. Move to safe area and press “Exchange” icon</strong></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-361\" src=\"https://mu.tienlinhmobile.games/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/z3992365879889_30598eaaf780d75db1e49a0e77242e08.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"624\" height=\"351\" /></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong>2. Use Diamonds to exchange exp</strong></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong>3. Use Zen to exchange exp</strong></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong>    <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">You can get more turn by up VIP</span></strong></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-359\" src=\"https://mu.tienlinhmobile.games/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/z3992365868698_e3c13be46b8c2bb008bbce335514551b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"624\" height=\"348\" /></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">V. PRAISING THE STATUE</span></strong></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong>A. Move to Lorencia Map and praising 7 Statue</strong></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong> - Statue of PVP King (110,95)</strong></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong> - Wolf Warlord Statue (110,88)</strong></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong> - Companion Statue (110,80) ; (102,80)</strong></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><span styl