(377, 1, '2022-12-27 15:23:57', '2022-12-27 08:23:57', '<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>I. QUEST</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<strong>A. MAIN QUEST</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>1. Press Avatar icon to open functions</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>2. Press Quest icon to open Quest manager</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-275 size-full\" src=\"https://mu.tienlinhmobile.games/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/z3991163604066_e07abfe0688d544fa9ed1b328bea2841.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"624\" height=\"349\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>3. Press “Main” to checking main quest</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>4. Press “Go” to doing</strong></p>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-278 size-full\" src=\"https://mu.tienlinhmobile.games/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/z3991164560277_e68f30012f21564395dbc799e79f6a26.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"624\" height=\"350\" /><strong><span id=\"input_part_0\" class=\"\" data-mention=\"5. Press here to automatic doing the Main quest \">5. Press here to automatic doing the Main quest </span></strong>\r\n<div id=\"input_line_2\"></div>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-280 size-full\" src=\"https://mu.tienlinhmobile.games/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/z3991164688422_88646d2f087150f2f786ae33bdc514f4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"624\" height=\"351\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>B. DAILY QUEST</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> 1. Press “Daily” to checking daily quest</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> 2. Press “Upgrade” to up star grade. The star grade more higher then the reward is bigger </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>3. Press “Go” to doing </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>4. Use Diamond to complete all Daily quest with five star grade and x2 rewards</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-282\" src=\"https://mu.tienlinhmobile.games/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/z3991165283566_6b016079ae3f9e707766626bbb1e351e.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"624\" height=\"350\" />\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div id=\"input_line_0\">\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">II. DUNGEON</span> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>A. DAILY DUNGEON</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> 1. Press “Dungeon” icon to open Dungeon list</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"input_line_3\"></div>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-284\" src=\"https://mu.tienlinhmobile.games/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/z3991165460786_601379d457d9ed0078ff03937049962a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"624\" height=\"350\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>2. Press “Daily Dungeon” to open daily dungeon list</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> 3. Press “EXP Dungeon” to choose the EXP dungeon</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-287\" src=\"https://mu.tienlinhmobile.games/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/z3991166616617_8e25f14334ce0d85c31ec6c78a3a9be8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"624\" height=\"350\" /><strong>4. Press “Enter” to going EXP Dungeon Map</strong>\r\n<div><strong>5. You have 03 turn going EXP Dungeon Map per day. It’ll reset at 00:00 every day or when you reborn.</strong></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\r\n<div><strong> 6. You can buy more 01 turn with VIP 3</strong></div>\r\n<div><strong>     You can buy more 02 turns with VIP 6</strong></div>\r\n<div><strong>     You can buy more 03 turns with VIP 9 </strong></div>\r\n<div>         <strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">WARNING: Use all turns before reborn</span></strong></div>\r\n<div id=\"input_line_6\"></div>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-289\" src=\"https://mu.tienlinhmobile.games/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/z3991167229007_c39d9392afbe32c114662b594e1bcbef.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"624\" height=\"348\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>B. SERVER DUNGEON</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>1. Press “Server Dungeon”</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>2. Press Dungeon map</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>3. Choose Team anh press “Quick Join” to join party</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>4. Create your party</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-327\" src=\"https://mu.tienlinhmobile.games/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/z3991167228259_b348e6f4ebaa022260366eca0182df10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"624\" height=\"350\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>5. Tick to request CP for your party</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> 6. Number of CP do you want to joint your party </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>7. Tick if you want automatically start when your party is full and ready</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> 8. Confirm create yor party</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-344\" src=\"https://mu.tienlinhmobile.games/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/z3991167228259_b348e6f4ebaa022260366eca0182df10-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"624\" height=\"350\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>9. Press send invitation to another player to join your party </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>10. Tick if you want automatically start when your party is full </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>11. Tick if you want to kick out any one unready in 30 second </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>12. Go to Dungeon Map </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>13. Leave your party</strong>\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340\" src=\"https://mu.tienlinhmobile.games/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/z3991167227294_662155402e0b794dc383c30e7508c183.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"624\" height=\"349\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Now, we have 5 Server Dungeon maps</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> 1. KALIMA</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> - Reborn 2 and level 15</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> - Number of turn per day: 1</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> - Suggested CP: 16.000 </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>2. ELEMENTAL WAR</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> - Reborn 3 and level 10</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> - Number of turn per day: 1</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> - Suggested CP: 20.000 </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>3. INFENAL CANYON </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>- Reborn 3 and level 60 </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>- Number of turn per day: 1 </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>- Suggested CP: 24.000 </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>4. HARMAGEDDON </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>- Reborn 4 and level 55 </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>- Number of turn per day: 1 </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>- Suggested CP: 38.000 </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>5. CRY WOLF </strong>\