=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong> - Companion Statue (110,80) ; (102,80)</strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong> - Majo League Champion Statue (98,85)</strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong> - Ruler of the Battlefield Statue (98,89)</strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong> - Battlefield Rules Statue (94,94)</strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong>B. Press “Event” icon -&gt; Press All server event -&gt; Press Fight for Resources</strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong>- Conquerer of the West Statue</strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong>- Akeron Underworld (101,134 )</strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong>- Conquerer of the East Statue</strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong>- Akeron Desert (96,122)</strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong>1. Use Zen to Praise </strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><strong>2.Use Diamonds to Praise (Get more exp)</strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" role=\"none\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">.</span></div>\r\n